Class NamedEnumUserType<E extends java.lang.Enum>

Type Parameters:

All Implemented Interfaces:
org.hibernate.usertype.ParameterizedType, org.hibernate.usertype.UserType
public class NamedEnumUserType<E extends java.lang.Enum>
extends AbstractEnumUserType<E,java.lang.String>

This class represent custom hibernate type that maps enum constants as strings. This string representation will be taken from NamedEnum.getName() method if enum implements this interface or from standard enum method Enum.name().

Since:
1.0
Author:
Ivan Khalopik
